===Korea=== {{Main article|Korean Peninsula}}[[File:Korea satelliet.jpg|thumb|Korean Peninsula]] The whole land mass encompassing North and South Korea is a peninsula, surrounded by the [[Sea of Japan]] on the east, the [[East China Sea]] to the south, and the [[Yellow Sea]] to the west, with the [[Korea Strait]] connecting the first two bodies of water.
